*.cpp\" --include=\"*.h\"\n过滤：系统头文件（<stdio.h>、<vector> 等尖括号形式）\n保留：引号形式（\"module/header.h\"）表示项目内依赖\n```\n\n### KMM\n\n**外部依赖：**\n```\nRead: build.gradle.kts\n提取 dependencies { } 块中的：\n  commonMainImplementation(...)\n  iosMainImplementation(...)\n  androidMainImplementation(...)\n```\n\n## 循环依赖检测\n\n检测模块间循环依赖（A → B → A）：\n\n1. 构建有向图：节点 = 模块，边 = 依赖关系\n2. 使用 DFS 检测环（记录访问路径，遇到已在路径中的节点即为循环）\n3. 输出格式：`⚠️ 循环依赖：ModuleA → ModuleB → ModuleA`\n\n**范围限制：** 仅检测项目内部模块间循环，不检测外部库。\n\n## 依赖图输出格式\n\n```\n## 外部依赖清单\n\n### CocoaPods (N 个)\n- Alamofire 5.9.1 — 网络请求\n- SnapKit 5.7.1 — AutoLayout DSL\n...\n\n### SPM (N 个)\n- swift-collections 1.0.4\n...\n\n## 内部模块依赖\n\n### NetworkModule\n依赖于：AuthModule、ConfigModule\n被依赖于：HomeFeature、ProfileFeature、OrderFeature\n\n### AuthModule\n依赖于：ConfigModule\n被依赖于：NetworkModule、LoginFeature\n\n## ⚠️ 循环依赖（若有）\n（无）\n```\n\n## 分析边界\n\n- 第三方库（Pods/、.build/、node_modules/）只列出名称和版本，不穿透进入\n- git submodule 作为独立模块标注，来源 URL 和版本 SHA 来自 INDEX.md 中已记录的 submodule 信息\n- 动态依赖注入（OC runtime、反射）标注「可能存在运行时依赖，静态分析无法覆盖」\n```\n\n## Context\n\nThis is the `project-reader` Claude Code plugin at `/Users/xpeng/.claude/plugins/local/project-reader/`. This is a **Markdown instruction file** — not executable code. The file tells Claude how to analyze dependencies when referenced as `@dep-analyzer`.\n\nExisting reference: `skills/core/entry-finder.md` follows this exact pattern (YAML frontmatter + methodology sections).\n\nThe file goes in: `skills/core/dep-analyzer.md`\n\nWorking directory: `/Users/xpeng/.claude/plugins/local/project-reader`\n\n## Your Job\n\n1. Write the file with the exact content specified above\n2. Verify: `cat skills/core/dep-analyzer.md | head -5` — should show the YAML frontmatter with `name: dep-analyzer`\n3. Commit:\n```bash\ncd /Users/xpeng/.claude/plugins/local/project-reader\ngit add skills/core/dep-analyzer.md\ngit commit -m \"feat(project-reader): add dep-analyzer methodology skill\n\n- Multi-language dependency parsing strategy (iOS/Python/C++/KMM)